MissionNotes:
This section contains all procedures read up to the crew during this mission.
It starts with the initial procedure communicated in Mission 16.


----------------



Initial LM to CSM power transfer procedure:

LM:
CB (11 and 16) - ASC ECA - CLOSE(2)
CB (11 and 16) - ASC ECA CONT - CLOSE(2)
BATT 5,6 NORM FEED - ON
BATT 1,3 - OFF/RESET
Wait 30 minutes for preconditioning
BATT 2,4 - OFF/RESET

CSM:
Connect LM/CSM umbilical
(5)CB - LM PWR-1 MN B - CLOSE
(5)CB - LM PWR-2 MN B - CLOSE
(5)CB EPS SENSOR SIGNAL MAIN B - CLOSE
(250) CB BATT B PWR ENTRY/POST LANDING - CLOSE
(275) CB MAIN B BATT BUS B - CLOSE
Verify Main Bus voltage
(2) LM PWR SW - CSM
(275) CB MAIN B BATT BUS B - OPEN
(250), CB BATT B PWR ENTRY/POST LANDING - OPEN
Verify Main Bus voltage

LM:
BATT 1,2,3 and 4 - HI VOLT - ON
BATT 5,6 - OFF
CB (11 and 16) - ASC ECA CONT - OPEN(2)


----------------


Updated LM to CSM power transfer procedure:


LM:
CB (11 and 16) - ASC ECA - CLOSE(2)
BATT 6 NORM FEED - ON
BATT 1,2,3 and 4 - OFF/RESET


CSM:
Connect LM/CSM umbilical
(5)CB - LM PWR-1 MN B - CLOSE
(5)CB - LM PWR-2 MN B - CLOSE
(5)CB EPS SENSOR SIGNAL MAIN B - CLOSE
(250) CB BATT B PWR ENTRY/POST LANDING - CLOSE
(275) CB MAIN B BATT BUS B - CLOSE
Verify Main Bus voltage
(2) LM PWR SW - CSM
(275) CB MAIN B BATT BUS B - OPEN
(250), CB BATT B PWR ENTRY/POST LANDING - OPEN
Verify Main Bus voltage

LM:
BATT 1,2,3 and 4 - HI VOLT - ON


----------------


Battery A charge

*| side is termination
250:
CB BATT A PWR ENTRY/POSTLANDING - CLOSE | --

275:
CB INVERTER PWR 2 MAIN B - CLOSE | OPEN

5:
CB BAT RELAY BUS BAT A - CLOSE | OPEN
CB EPS SENSOR UNIT AC BUS 2 - CLOSE | OPEN
CB EPS SENSOR SIGNAL AC-2 - CLOSE | OPEN
CB BATTERY CHARGER MN B - CLOSE | OPEN
CB BATTERY CHARGER AC PWR - CLOSE | OPEN
CB BATTERY CHARGER BAT A CHG - CLOSE | OPEN
CB INVERTER CONTROL 2 - CLOSE | OPEN
CB INVERTER CONTROL 3 - CLOSE | OPEN
SW MAIN BUS TIE A/C - OFF | --
SW BAT CHARGE - AC-2 | AC-1

3:
SW AC INVERTER 2 - MNB | --
SW INVERTER 2 AC BUS 2 - ON (UP) | OFF
SW AC BUS 2 RESET - RESET (CENTER) | OFF
SW BATTERY CHARGE - A
SW DC INDICATOR SEL - BAT CHARGER | MN-B


----------------


Power removal from CM/LM umbilical:

CSM:
LM PWR 2 - OPEN
LM PWR 1 - OPEN
EPS SENSOR SIGNAL CB MAIN B - OPEN

LM:
CB(16) EPS: BAT FEED TIE (2) - OPEN
BAT 1 HV - OFF/RESET
BAT 2 LV - OFF/RESET THEN ON
BAT 2 HV - OFF/RESET THEN ON
BAT 1 HV - ON
CB(16) EPS: BAT FEED TIE (2) - CLOSE


----------------


Battery charge reverse procedure
3:
SW BATTERY CHARGE - OFF
SW AC INVERTER 2 - OFF

5:
SW MAIN BUS TIE BAT B/C - ON (UP)

250:
CB BAT A PWR ENTRY/POSTLANDING - OPEN
CB BAT B PWR ENTRY/POSTLANDING - OPEN

5:
CB BATTERY CHARGER BAT B CHG - OPEN
